'''尼古拉斯·安東尼·「尼克」·格林'''（{{lang-en|Nicholas Anthony "Nick" Green}}，{{bd|1978年|9月10日|||Green, Nick}}），[[佛羅里達州|佛羅里達州]][[彭薩科拉|彭薩科拉市]]人，美国棒球运动员，曾是[[美國職棒大聯盟|美國職棒大聯盟]]的[[內野手|內野手]]。

==職業生涯==
格林畢業於喬治亞佩雷米特學院<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://mlb.mlb.com/team/player_career.jsp?player_id=407797 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2009-04-09 |archive-date=2008-04-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080411105728/http://mlb.mlb.com/team/player_career.jsp?player_id=407797 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，並在1998年的[[大聯盟|大聯盟]][[選秀|選秀]]大會上第32輪被[[亞特蘭大勇士|亞特蘭大勇士]]隊選中<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.thebaseballcube.com/draft/1998/June-Reg/32.shtml |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2009-04-09 |archive-date=2009-06-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090607082036/http://www.thebaseballcube.com/draft/1998/June-Reg/32.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2004年，格林代表勇士隊首度登上大聯盟。2005年，他被交易到[[坦帕灣光芒|坦帕灣魔鬼魚]]隊；這年他在魔鬼魚隊出賽111場，繳出[[打擊率|打擊率]]2成39、[[全壘打|全壘打]]5支和[[打點|打點]]29分的成績。之後幾個賽季格林輾轉多支球隊。

2009年1月5日，格林和[[波士頓紅襪|波士頓紅襪]]隊簽下[[小聯盟|小聯盟]]合約，並邀請他參加大聯盟春訓<ref>{{cite web | url = http://soxanddawgs.com/2009/01/05/red-sox-sign-nick-green/ | title = Red Sox Sign Nick Green | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090902001532/http://soxanddawgs.com/2009/01/05/red-sox-sign-nick-green/ | archivedate = 2009-09-02 }}</ref>。後來由於[[胡裡奧·盧戈|胡裡奧·盧戈]]的受傷，格林進入紅襪隊開季25人名單，擔任[[游擊手|游擊手]]<ref>{{cite web | url = http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20090331&content_id=4095190&vkey=news_bos&fext=.jsp&c_id=bos | title = Carter, Green on verge of making club | author = Ian Browne | publisher = MLB.com | date = 2009-03-31 | accessdate = 2009-04-09 | archive-date = 2009-04-03 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20090403092422/http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20090331&content_id=4095190&vkey=news_bos&fext=.jsp&c_id=bos | dead-url = no }}</ref>。8月27日對戰[[芝加哥白襪|芝加哥白襪]]隊的比賽中，格林客串[[投手|投手]]主投2局，雖然投出3次[[保送|保送]]，但沒有被擊出任何[[安打|安打]]，也沒有失分<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.boston.com/sports/baseball/redsox/articles/2009/08/27/red_sox_green_pitches_for_first_time_in_majors/ | title = Red Sox' Green pitches for first time in majors | publisher = Boston.com | date = 2009-08-27 | accessdate = 2009-08-28 | archive-date = 2009-08-31 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20090831113324/http://www.boston.com/sports/baseball/redsox/articles/2009/08/27/red_sox_green_pitches_for_first_time_in_majors/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

